{"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNSymbolStyleLayer(py)textVariableAnchorOffset","fragments":[{"text":"textVariableAnchorOffset","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","symbolKind":"property","title":"textVariableAnchorOffset","roleHeading":"Instance Property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"}]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"To increase the chance of placing high-priority labels on the map, you can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provide an array of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textAnchor"},{"type":"text","text":" locations, each paired with an offset value."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The renderer will attempt to place the label at each location, in order, before"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"moving on to the next location+offset. Use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"textJustify: auto"},{"type":"text","text":" to choose"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"justification based on anchor position."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSExpression","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSExpression"},{"kind":"text","text":" * "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"textVariableAnchorOffset"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The length of the array must be even, and must alternate between enum and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"point entries. i.e., each anchor location must be accompanied by a point, and","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"that point defines the offset when th